{"tid":1898734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心身體呀 今日日頭有成28度","createTime":"2020-02-26T08:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T19:50:20.000Z","uid":240448,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"efb899d4a19fc0124c6c68ca50ce2fe2b81c1623","tid":1898734,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBobJ6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBobJ6G.jpg&h=c7951a38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRGHQMH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRGHQMH.jpg&h=2e10fc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[天氣速報] 受一股海洋氣流影響，明日日間天氣相當溫暖，市區最高氣溫約27度，新界再高一兩度。一股達強風程度的偏東氣流會在本週後期影響廣東沿岸，屆時風勢較大。隨著偏東氣流再度被海洋氣流取代，週末日間再度變得相當溫暖。大家要留意，外套仍然未可以收埋住，下週中期天氣顯著轉涼，天氣仍然乍暖還寒，要小心保重身體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[天氣速報] 本港今日天氣相當溫暖，天文台總部錄得最高氣溫為28.1度，為二月的第二高紀錄。九龍城以及新界北部氣溫更超過30度。"},{"pid":"50693fa047f6c7319315336f7a78f8baead83fde","tid":1898734,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"From 巴打氣象台"},{"pid":"c75d2a79db7e8dc3fd1407f4156e4e6e04aed292","tid":1898734,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"繼續升，希望無曬d肺炎病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365889c4b27ec0cc5c089969cd7b3fb7e33627f8","tid":1898734,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75d2a79db7e8dc3fd1407f4156e4e6e04aed292","tid":1898734,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"繼續升，希望無曬d肺炎病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"希望如此 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as